OL,3,CEsther Rantzen would choose to die in
OL,4,CJersey if law changes
OL,6,FThe - a person must be 18 or over,
OL,7,Fliving in Jersey for at least a year
OL,8,Fand either have a terminal illness or
OL,9,Fhave been diagnosed with an incurable
OL,10,Fphysical condition that causes
OL,11,F"unbearable suffering".
OL,13,FDame Esther says: "I think it only
OL,14,Fcomes to the front of your mind when,
OL,15,Flike me, you have a terminal illness
OL,16,For something happens in your life
OL,17,Fwhich means you are suffering intense
OL,18,Fpain and you want to be eased out of
OL,19,Fthis life.
