OL,3,CEsther Rantzen would choose to die in
OL,4,CJersey if law changes
OL,6,FThey also believe it goes against the
OL,7,Fethics of medical professionals to do
OL,8,Fno harm and could lead to the law
OL,9,Fbeing expanded later down the line, a
OL,10,Fso-called 'slippery slope'.
OL,12,FJersey residents with - a majority are
OL,13,Fin favour of 'Route 1' for people with
OL,14,Fa terminal illness but there is around
OL,15,Fa 50-50 split on support for 'Route
OL,16,F2', those with "unbearable suffering".
